contact me anytime.

147
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,680
Hahaha.

148
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,240
Sure.

149
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,040
Hey.

150
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,920
