185
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,639
When I was little,

186
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,879
I will stargaze

187
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,960
here

188
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,039
at night

189
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,559
whenever I feel down.

190
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,679
Do you like it?

191
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:57,799
Yes.

192
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,080
What's on your mind?

193
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,000
I'm wondering

194
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,120
