201
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,320
My grandfather said

202
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:43,960
I need to be brave and strong
all the more precisely because

203
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,519
I'm a girl.

204
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,799
Can you

205
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,120
stay here with me tonight?

206
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,519
Don't overthink it.

207
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,039
I just feel

208
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,600
a little lonely right now.

